          <caption>
            <p>Percent of error (relative to Kew 1Cx) obtained for genome size predictions for 6 genome size estimators on 8 plant sequencing datasets, with various sequencing depths of coverage. Plant species are ordered from left to right from the lowest to the highest sequencing depth as displayed in the “depth of coverage” panel: points are connected for easier visualization.</p>
